span>"},{"pid":"752cad2bb91b81c4d53255a9e25a6e63cafa982f","tid":1457042,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:21:40.000Z","msg":"團結啊！<br />\n不割啊！<br />\n今日中招嗰啲我相信會自我反省，唔好再鬧佢哋，佢哋知錯架啦！<br />\n諗下下一步做咩啦！<br />\n永不割席"},{"pid":"276120d3fdc1fd728135e6303dab67540a0234bf","tid":1457042,"uid":79085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:21:51.000Z","msg":"其實係因為情報有時間差係到<br />\n一開始有狗未停飛 唔駛走<br />\n而家停左抵港 但仲有轉機客未清<br />\n清哂之前要散水"},{"pid":"98f2d05fb64801779eea0b5b261c154b34f51a3f","tid":1457042,"uid":78352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:21:59.000Z","msg":"當初既現場決定呢"},{"pid":"d46e3b4b5b8cf31192b4e49fd224f8f4f6a54644","tid":1457042,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:22:15.000Z","msg":"大家會有意見不合正常嘅，不過唔好太離譜。留守的人認為警察係正常，唔會係有旅客的情況下做咩；叫走嘅人係認為警察會喺有旅客嘅情況下依然繼續清場行動，又或者係一啲引入示威者裏面搞旅行嘅人"},{"pid":"ae9b052464f496eeef78252dcd73956004202bdb","tid":1457042,"uid":263730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd5e034d66c8b7fddaf339024fcc844a7c874a51","tid":1457042,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:25:14.000Z","msg":"無計 資訊一面倒<br />\n要改變心態唔係咁易<br />\n<br />\n起馬今日做到cancel晒六點後離港航班<br />\n<br />\n第一次面對話機場清場係恐慌啲嫁嘞<br />\n有咗經驗 現場會更識fact check啲<br />\n<br />\n同埋大家要小心資訊"},{"pid":"a368f0cfe8a96d817688fa0cabcc31a5a7fbeffc","tid":1457042,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c35855a7ba1ecc778c1e8d423f9c9e62d905dfc8","tid":1457042,"uid":66357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:19:34.000Z","msg":"鳩僧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}